Hi everyone, hope this is the correct channel to ask my question.

I want to edit our marketplace listing but when I start the edit, it does not list all the “App features” that are already listed on our live listing. There should be 4 features but it says only 1 in the top header, when I go to “App features” there is no feature listed. I tried deleting the drafts but it didn’t work.

How can I start to edit the listing from the version that is live?
